saudi drop condit for oil sale to brazil saudi arabia ha drop it condit that brazil secur intern bank guarant befor saudia arabia would ship it oil , state-oil compani petrobra said in a statement . petrobra said the saudi will accept banco do brasil credit guarant . petrobra cancel a 40 mln dlr crude oil purcha from the saudi yesterday after they refu to accept a letter of credit from the offici bank of brazil . the saudi had demand that brazil get credit guarant from lead intern bank . petrobra said the saudi had been advi that if they did not chang their mind by monday , petrobra would negoti the purcha of oil with other produc . the petrobra statement said the shipment of 2.2 mln barrel will be made by the saudi on march 24 as schedul . the shipment wa part of a contract sign in februari for the saudi to suppli brazil with 125,000 barrel per day until june .